表格报警资料的代码预览

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('AlarmInfo')
and type = 'U')
drop table AlarmInfo
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: AlarmInfo */
/*==============================================================*/
create table AlarmInfo (
ID int identity(1,1),
AlarmSource Domain_2 not null,
AlarmMachine varchar(20) not null,
DutyOn varchar(20) not null,
AlarmMemo varchar(200) not null,
AlarmStatus bit null,
SendType bit null,
AlarmTotalTime decimal(4, 2) null,
CreateDate datetime null,
Remark varchar(200) null,
IsReadFlag varchar(1) null constraint DF_AlarmInfo_Flag default (0)
)
ON [PRIMARY]
END
go

declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'0为未报警,1为已报警',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'AlarmInfo', 'column', 'AlarmStatus'
go
